{"article_id":"HGcqn6N0ICgvRlQ5","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Several mainstream media outlets reported Friday","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"that the U.S. government recently confirmed","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"that Russian government `` cyber actors '' attempted to hack the 2016 election results or `` election systems . '' JUST IN :","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"\" Russian government cyber actors \" unsuccessfully attempted to hack 2016 election results in Wisconsin ,","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"DHS tells state officials","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"pic.twitter.com/PMd6Gj5z4b","depth":4},{"id":6,"text":"- NBC Politics","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"( @ NBCPolitics )","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"September 22 , 2017","depth":4},{"id":9,"text":"However , the tweets do n't correctly characterize what the Department of Homeland Security said about Russia 's actions ,","depth":3},{"id":10,"text":"giving readers a very misguided idea of what actually happened .","depth":3},{"id":11,"text":"The DHS said","depth":4},{"id":12,"text":"that 21 states were affected .","depth":4},{"id":13,"text":"But it was n't election results or voting machines that the Russians attempted to manipulate , but rather the voter registrations systems ,","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"according to Wisconsin officials , one of the effected states .","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"`` This afternoon , the U.S. Department of Homeland Security notified the Wisconsin Elections Commission for the first time","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"that 'Russia government cyber actors ' unsuccessfully targeted the state 's voter registration system in 2016 , ''","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"the officials said in a statement .","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"They explained","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"the attempts had `` no impact on Wisconsin ' s systems or the election . ''","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"The Hill further explained","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"why voting machine or election results can not be tampered with :","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"In the majority of the states , the Department of Homeland Security only saw preparations for hacking , like scanning","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"to find potential modes for attack .","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"Voting machines are not connected to the internet","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"and can not be scanned in this way ,","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"but other systems ,","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"including those","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"housing voter rolls ,","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"can be .","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"Jessica Huseman , a reporter for ProPublica , called NBC out on social media for the error :","depth":4},{"id":31,"text":"This is false .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"It says nothing","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"- Nothing -","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"about `` election results . ''","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"Registration systems are disconnected from the results .","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"https : //t.co/vcWCXUipm9","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"- Jessica Huseman","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"( @ JessicaHuseman )","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"September 22 , 2017","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"I 'm not going to hold my breath on @ NBCPolitics writing a correction here","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"-","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"though they absolutely should .","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"- Jessica Huseman","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"( @ JessicaHuseman )","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"September 22 , 2017","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"This is a flatly irresponsible tweet","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"& it is stunning that an organization","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"that reports about elections","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"does not know how these systems work","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"- Jessica Huseman","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"( @ JessicaHuseman )","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"September 22 , 2017","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":105,"left":63,"right":104,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":63,"left"